      • setPermuteResults

        public TriangleListingBase<K,VV,EV,R> setPermuteResults(boolean permuteResults)
        By default only one result is output for each triangle, whether vertices are sorted or unsorted. When permutation is enabled a result is instead output for each of the six permutations of the three vertex IDs.
        参数:
        permuteResults - whether output results should be permuted
        返回:
        this

      • setSortTriangleVertices

        public TriangleListingBase<K,VV,EV,R> setSortTriangleVertices(boolean sortTriangleVertices)
        Normalize the triangle listing such that for each result (K0, K1, K2) the vertex IDs are sorted K0 < K1 < K2.
        参数:
        sortTriangleVertices - whether to output each triangle's vertices in sorted order
        返回:
        this
